//┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏
/*! 
   @brief 強制エンカウント 共通
   
   @param       s32PlayerTag        プレイヤータグ
   @param       s32TargetCharaTag	ターゲット
   @author      Yuki-Kozai
*/
//┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏┏
function forceEncount(s32PlayerTag, s32TargetCharaTag)
{
	local temp = [ 
		ECT_FIELDMAP_CHARA_SET_EVENT_MODE, s32PlayerTag,
		ECT_FIELDMAP_CHARA_COLLISION_FLAG, s32PlayerTag, 0, 0, 1, 2,
		ECT_FIELDMAP_CHARA_SET_EVENT_MODE, s32TargetCharaTag,
		ECT_FIELDMAP_CHARA_COLLISION_FLAG, s32TargetCharaTag, 0, 0, 1, 2,
		
		//ECT_CAMERA_C_TYPE_SET, CAMERA_C_MANUAL, 
		//ECT_CAMERA_AT_MOVE_SET, OBJ_TYPE_CHARA_SELF, s32TargetCharaTag, MODEL_OFFSET_FACE, 0,-10,50, MOVE_FIX_ACCEL, 80, 100, 
		//ECT_CAMERA_LENGTH_MOVE_SET, 700, 80, CURVE_SPEED_DOWN, 

		//ECT_MACRO_TIME_WAIT, 50, 

		ECT_CHARA_ROT_MOVE_SET_TARGET, s32TargetCharaTag, OBJ_TYPE_CHARA_SELF, s32PlayerTag, MODEL_OFFSET_FOOT, 0,0,0, 40, CURVE_SPEED_DOWN,
		ECT_CHARA_ROT_MOVE_SET_TARGET, s32PlayerTag, OBJ_TYPE_CHARA_SELF, s32TargetCharaTag, MODEL_OFFSET_FOOT, 0,0,0, 40, CURVE_SPEED_DOWN,
		ECT_CHARA_ROT_MOVE_WAIT, s32TargetCharaTag,

		//ECT_CAMERA_C_TYPE_SET, CAMERA_C_MANUAL,
		//ECT_CAMERA_EYEAT_POS_SET, OBJ_TYPE_CHARA_SELF, s32TargetCharaTag, MODEL_OFFSET_BODY, 0,-10,0, OBJ_TYPE_CHARA_SELF, s32TargetCharaTag, MODEL_OFFSET_BODY, 0,40,200, 
		//ECT_CAMERA_AT_MOVE_SET, OBJ_TYPE_CHARA_SELF, s32TargetCharaTag, MODEL_OFFSET_BODY, 0,-10,0, MOVE_FIX_ACCEL, 50, 100, 
		//ECT_CAMERA_EYE_MOVE_SET, OBJ_TYPE_CHARA_SELF, s32TargetCharaTag, MODEL_OFFSET_BODY, -50,100,800, MOVE_FIX_ACCEL, 50, 100,

		ECT_CHARA_MOTION_SET, s32TargetCharaTag, MOTION_EX10, 0, 1000, 
		ECT_CHARA_MOTION_SET_SPEED, s32TargetCharaTag, 80, 

		ECT_CHARA_MOTION_SET, s32PlayerTag, MOTION_F_BATTLE, 0, 30, 
		ECT_CHARA_MOTION_WAIT, s32PlayerTag, 
		ECT_CHARA_MOTION_SET, s32PlayerTag, MOTION_F_BATTLE, 1, 0,

		ECT_CHARA_MOTION_WAIT, s32TargetCharaTag,
		ECT_MACRO_CHARA_WAIT, s32TargetCharaTag,
		
		ECT_FIELDMAP_CHARA_COLLISION_FLAG, s32PlayerTag, 1, 1, 1, 2,
		ECT_FIELDMAP_CHARA_COLLISION_FLAG, s32TargetCharaTag, 1, 1, 1, 2,
		
		ECT_END
	];
	
	foreach (idx, val in temp) {
		SQ.copyProgramMacro(val, idx);
	}
	
	SQ.execProgramMacro("forceEncount");
	
	return;
}

